name: "MVC Portlet with DS and JSP"
description: |
  Demonstrates how to 
    <ul> 
      <li> build a portlet with Liferay MVC framework </li>
      <li> use DS (Declarative Services) framework to register it </li>
      <li> use JSPs for the view </li>
      <li> use language resource bundles </li>
    </ul>
displayFiles:
  - name: Documentation 
    highlighting: markdown 
    path: README.md
  - name: Portlet class
    highlighting: java 
    path: src/main/java/com/liferay/code/samples/portal/modules/applications/portlets/mvc_ds_jsp/JSPPortlet.java
  - name: The JSP view
    highlighting: java 
    path: src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/view.jsp
  - name: Bnd configuration
    highlighting: yaml 
    path: bnd.bnd
  - name: Maven POM
    highlighting: xml 
    path: pom.xml
  - name: Gradle build
    highlighting: groovy 
    path: build.gradle
